cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on building 3D models using a robot platform and manipulating objects for better classification. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper discusses processing visual data from different viewpoints and removing background noise. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is likely as the paper mentions learning new object categories as they are encountered, which involves machine learning techniques. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely for the same reason as cs.AI. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper involves controlling a mobile manipulation robot equipped with an RGBD camera.
